#CHIP AY8910
#CLOCK 1789773

; AY8910 (General Instrument AY-3-8910) Envelope Generator Test
;
; The AY8910 PSG chip has 3 tone channels and 1 noise channel.
; Each channel has an envelope generator that can produce various shapes.
;
; Tests:
; - All 4 envelope modes (\, /, /\, custom)
; - Envelope period and shape
; - Volume tracking with envelopes

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Tone channel 1 with envelope (sawtooth: /\ )
c4 . . .

r4

; Tone channel 2 with different envelope (inverted sawtooth: \/)
d4 . . .

r4

; Tone channel 3 with ramp up (/)  
e4 . . .

r4

; All 3 tone channels with envelopes
c4 & d4 & e4 .

r4

; Envelope with long sustained notes
c4 _ _ _ d4 _ _ _

r2

#END
